(256, 'Anjo Snail Foam Cleansing', '#256', 8, '<p>Description</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Anjo] snail foam cleansing 150ml</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mild and soft cleanser that turns from snail mucus foam into soft bubble-like cream that provides deep pore cleansing for clear and moisturized skin Cleanses Skin, deep pores, dead skin, and rids of blackheads, sebum, and waste for clear, moisturized skin Mild and soft cleanser that turns from snail mucus foam into soft bubble-like cream that provides deep pore cleansing for clear and moisturized skin</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&bull;A rejuvenating foaming facial wash for smooth, shine-free skin.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;Softens and moisturizes skin with snail slime ultra-filtrate</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;Helps keep your face sparkling clear and bright</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;Gently cleanses to remove dirt, oil, and dead skin cells</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull;Melts away impurities and removes makeup</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ingredients; Snail mucus filtrate</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How to Use</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Put an appropriate amount on the plam of your hand and make a sufficient foam , then gently wipe like a massage all over the face and then wash off with lukewarm water.</p>', 700.00, 800.00, 100, 'in', 'Anjo-Fome-Cleansing-1638859530.png', NULL, 'Skin Care', 1, 'Anjo Fome Cleansing', 'Anjo Fome Cleansing', NULL, 1, 1, '2021-12-07 06:45:31', '2021-12-21 06:16:08'),
(257, 'Purito Defence Barrier PH Cleanser', '#257', 8, '<p>Description</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PURITO Defence Barrier Ph Cleanser 150ml / 5.07 fl.oz. Protect your skin barrier using a mildly acidic cleanser with pH 5.5. This refreshing gel cleanser transforms into a rich foam that gently cleanses the skin. This cleanser is ideal for daily use in the morning and night. It is a gentle cleanser suitable for sensitive and dry skin. It will not strip the skin of its natural moisture and will leave the skin hydrated. *The above description is limited to raw material characteristics.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How to Use</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Put a small amount in your palm, add water and create a foam. Apply on damp skin and gently massage onto face and neck in circular motions. Rinse clean with lukewarm water.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ingredients</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Water, Coco-Betaine (cleansing agents), Sodium Lauroyl Methyl Isethionate (cleansing agents), Arginine(pH Adjusters), Sodium Chloride(Viscosity Increasing Agents), Betaine(Humectants), Acrylates/C10-30 Alkyl Acrylate Crosspolymer(Viscosity Increasing Agents), Hydroxyacetophenone(Antioxidants), Sodium Methyl Isethionate(cleansing agents), Lauric Acid(cleansing agents), Centella Asiatica Extract (skin-conditioning agents), Sodium Laurate(cleansing agents), Melaleuca Alternifolia (Tea Tree) Leaf Oil(Skin-Conditioning Agents), Ethylhexylglycerin(skin-conditioning agents), Allantoin (skin protectants), Disodium EDTA (stabilizer), 1,2-Hexanediol(Solvents)</p>', 1250.00, 1350.00, 100, 'in', 'Purito-Defence-Barrier-PH-Cleanser-1638859974.png', NULL, 'Skin Care', 1, 'Purito Defence Barrier PH Cleanser Orginal Korean', 'Purito Defence Barrier PH Cleanser Orginal Korean', NULL, 1, 1, '2021-12-07 06:52:55', '2021-12-19 07:33:31'),
