(267, '3w Lemon Hand Cream Orginal Korean', '#267', 8, '<p>Description The Lemon Extract with excellent moisturizing effect quickly absorb on the skin and supply moist on the skin and form skin protection layer so it makes the rough hands to soft and smooth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How To Use: After washing your hands, take adequate amount and apply along the skin texture so it will absorb well. Contens: 100 ml by Royal Wellness</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ingredients: Water, Mineral Oil, Cetearyl Alcohol, Polysorbate 60, Carbomer, Triethanolamine,Phenoxyethanol, Methylparaben, Sorbitan Sesquioleate, Propylparaben, Citrus Limon(Lemon)Fruit Extrct,Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Extract, Cornus Officinalis Fruit Extract, Chaenomeles Sinensis Fruit Extract, Yellow 5(CI 19140), Perfum.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Features &amp; details It helps lighten dull skin and smooth out uneven skin texture while moisturizing, like a lemon brusting on your hand Delicately scented hydrating hand cream Make it soft and smooth like silk Provides intensive moisture For soft hands</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Enter</p>', 500.00, 650.00, 100, 'in', '3w-Lemon-Hand-Cream-1638938923.png', NULL, 'Hand Cream', 1, '3w Lemon Hand Cream Orginal Korean', '3w Lemon Hand Cream Orginal Korean', NULL, 1, 1, '2021-12-08 04:48:44', '2021-12-19 06:37:57'),
(268, 'Platinum Horse Oil Hand Cream', '#268', 8, '<p>Contains horse oil ingredients and all kinds of extracts which helps to keep your skin soft and supple by way of forming external layers of the skin that prevents loss of moisture</p>', 500.00, 650.00, 100, 'in', 'Platinum-Horse-Oil-Hand-Cream-Orginal-Korean-1638939198.png', NULL, 'Hand Cream', 1, 'Platinum Horse Oil Hand Cream Orginal Korean', 'Platinum Horse Oil Hand Cream Orginal Korean', NULL, 1, 1, '2021-12-08 04:53:19', '2021-12-18 10:16:33'),
(269, 'Dabo Lemon Brightening Skin Relief Hand Cream Orginal Korean', '#269', 8, '<p>How to Use: After wash your hand and fell dry, apply suitable amount of hand cream over the back of the hand and fingers, nails.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Features &amp; details DABO Skin Relief Hand Cream - Lemon - Light and soft texture of the product absorbs fast, creating moisturizing shield over the skin and soothing naturally coarse and dry hands without excessive stickiness. It contains excellent lemon for moisture retention and sedation, so it can be kept glossy and comfortable for a long time and the fresh lemon fragrance stays on your skin, giving you a refreshing feel Product information</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ingredients : Water, Mineral Oil, Glycerin, Butylene Glycol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Polysorbate 60, Carbomer, Triethanolamine, Sorbitan Sesquioleate, Phenoxyethanol, Propylparaben, Methylparaben, Citrus Limon (Lemon) Fruit Extract(100mg), Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Extract, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Extract, Camellia Sinensis Leaf Extract, Fragrance, Allantoin, Disodium EDTA</p>\r\n\r\n<p>weight; 100ml.</p>', 500.00, 650.00, 100, 'in', 'Dabo-Lemon-Brightening-Skin-Relief-Hand-Cream-1639027667.png', NULL, 'Hand Cream', 1, 'Dabo Lemon Brightening Skin Relief Hand Cream Orginal Korean', 'Dabo Lemon Brightening Skin Relief Hand Cream Orginal Korean', NULL, 1, 1, '2021-12-09 05:27:48', '2021-12-18 10:10:44'),
