(273, 'Rice Water Bright Foaming Cleanser Orginal Korean', '#273', 8, '<p>About</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Detoxify, brighten and cleanse Experience smoother, softer and brighter skin with Rice Water Bright Cleansing Foam from The Face Shop. The rich, creamy texture provides a detoxifying cleanse, removing impurities, dead skin cells and makeup. Enriched with natural ingredients, like fermented rice extract and soapwort extract, the cleansing foam leaves skin looking clean, clear and bright.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How To Use: Apply adequate amount to hands and work into luxurious lather. Gently massage onto wet skin using circular motions. After thoroughly cleansing your face, wash off with cool water. Use morning and night.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ingredients</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Water/Eau, Myristic Acid, Glycerin, Potassium Hydroxide, Stearic Acid, Glycol, Distearate, Lauric Acid, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Cocamide Mea, Disodium Cocoamphodiacetate, Glyceryl, Stearate, Peg-100 Stearate, Sodium Lauryl Sulfate, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Extract, Saponaria Officinalis Leaf Extract, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Bran Oil, Titanum Dioxide (CI 77891), Sodium Chloride, Divinyldimethicone/Dimethicone Copolymer, C12-14 Pareth-23, C12-13 Pareth, Hexylene Glycol, Disodium Edta, Blue 1 (CI 42090), Yellow 5 (CI 19140), Red 4 (CI 14700), Hydroxypropyl Methylcellulose, Sodium Benzoate, Parfum/ Fragranc</p>', 1050.00, 1150.00, 100, 'in', 'Rice-Water-Bright-Foaming-Cleanser-1639549050.png', 'Rice-Water-Bright-Foaming-Cleanser-Orginal-Korean-1639680747-1.png', 'Skin Care', 1, 'Rice Water Bright Foaming Cleanser Orginal Korean', 'Rice Water Bright Foaming Cleanser Orginal Korean', NULL, 1, 1, '2021-12-15 06:17:31', '2021-12-23 07:54:59');
